# Amplitude Product Suite

Amplitude is a comprehensive product analytics platform that helps businesses understand user behavior, optimize product experiences, and drive growth through data-driven insights. The platform consists of several integrated products designed to work together to provide a complete solution for product teams.

## Key Products and Features

### Analytics
Amplitude's core analytics platform provides behavioral analytics and AI automation to help users answer growth questions without coding. It unifies data to facilitate product improvement and offers no-code analytics capabilities, allowing teams to:
- Track and analyze user behavior
- Identify patterns and trends
- Make data-driven product decisions
- Measure product performance

### Data
Amplitude Data provides tools for data integration, identity resolution across devices, and customer/product data management. Key capabilities include:
- Data integration across tech stacks
- Cross-device identity resolution and tracking
- Data quality tools and validation
- Customer data management
- Product data control
- Data warehouse native integration

### Experiment
Amplitude Experiment enables product teams to run controlled experiments to optimize product features and user experiences:
- Feature flagging for controlled rollouts
- A/B testing to compare variations
- Multivariate experiments for testing multiple variables
- Multi-armed Bandit experiments for optimization
- Remote configuration management
- Web experimentation (codeless experimentation)

### Web Experiment
A specialized feature within Experiment that allows running A/B, multivariate, and Multi-armed bandit experiments on websites without coding. It includes:
- Code-free experimentation capabilities
- Advanced targeting options
- Performance optimization
- Impression tracking
- Post-experiment actions
- Landing page and conversion optimization

### Session Replay
This qualitative analytics tool records and plays back user sessions to:
- Visualize user journeys
- Synchronize with event streams
- Diagnose bugs and issues
- Analyze user experience
- Share replays with team members
- Apply search filters to find specific sessions

### Guides and Surveys
An alternative to popup components for improving user experience, helping to:
- Create in-app messaging
- Facilitate user onboarding
- Collect product feedback
- Optimize user journeys
- Improve key metrics like retention, activation, and engagement
- Enable cross-functional team collaboration

### CDP (Customer Data Platform)
A customer data platform natively integrated with analytics that helps:
- Proactively improve data quality
- Discover new audiences
- Sync behavioral data across your technology stack

